quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  21,51,Futhi khumbula ngempela samnikeza u-Abrahamu ukuholwa kwakhe ngaphambilini futhi sasazi kahle ngaye
  21,52,Ngenkathi ethi kuyise nakubantu bakhe “iyini lemifanekiso enizinikele kuyona na
  21,53,"Bathi, “sabafumana obaba bethu beyikhonza (lemifanekiso)”"
  21,54,"Wathi, “Ngempela nina uqobo lwenu nobaba benu nanisekudukeni okucacile”"
  21,55,"Bathi, “Ngakube usilethele iqiniso noma wena ungomunye walabo abenza umdlalo na?”"
  21,56,"(U-Abrahamu) wathi, “Qha! INkosi yenu yiNkosi yamazulu nomhlaba okuyiyona eyawadala futhi mina kulokho ngingomunye walabo abafakazayo”"
  21,57,Futhi (ngiyafunga) ngoMvelinqangi ngempela ngizozenzela isu izithixo zenu emva kokuba senifulathele senihambile”
  21,58,Ngakho-ke (u-Abrahamu) waziphihlisa (izithixo) zaba yizicucu ngaphandle kwesikhulu sazo ukuze babuyele kusona (basibuze)
  21,59,"(Babuza) bathi, “ngubani owenze lokhu konkulunkulu bethu na? Ngempela yena ungomunye wabangalungile”"
  21,60,Bathi “simzwile umfanyana ongu-Abrahamu ekhuluma ngabo”
  21,61,"Bathi, “mletheni lapha ngaphambi kwamehlo abantu, ukuze bambone”"
  21,62,"(Bambuza) bathi, “ngakube nguwena owenze lokhu konkulunkulu bethu Oh Abraham na!?”"
  21,63,"(U-Abraham) wathi, “Qha okwenzile ilesi (sithixo) esikhulu sazo ngakho-ke zibuzeni (izithixo) uma zikwazi ukukhuluma”"
  21,64,"Base bephendukela emiphefumulweni yabo base bethi, “ngempela nina uqobo lwenu niyizoni”"
  21,65,Base becabanga kabusha (bathi) “ngempela wazile ukuthi izithixo lezi azikhulumi”
  21,66,Wathi “ngakube nikhonza okunye esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi lokho okunganisizi ngalutho futhi okunganilimazi na?”
  21,67,Okubi phezu kwenu kanye nakulokho enikhonzayo esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi ngakube aninamqondo yini na
  21,68,"Bathi, “Mshiseni, nelekelele onkulunkulu benu uma nifuna ukwenza (okuthize)”"
  21,69,"Sathi, “Oh Mlilo! banda, ungabi nobungozi ku-Abrahamu”"
  21,70,Futhi babemfunela icebo ngakho-ke sabenza abalahlekelwa ngokwedlulele
  21,71,Futhi samsindisa kanye noLoti sabaletha ezweni esalibusisa emihlabeni
  21,72,Futhi samupha u-Isak no-Jakobe njengesipho (indodana yendodana) futhingamunyewabosamenzawabangolungileyo
  21,73,Futhi sabenza ukuthi babengabaholi abahola ngempoqo yethu futhi sazembula kubona izenzo ezinhle nokwenza umthandazo nokukhokha izakaah (ingxenye yemali ekhokhwa kwabampofu) futhi babeyizikhonzi zethu
  21,74,"Futhi uLothi samnikeza ukwehlulela nolwazi futhi samsindisa edolobheni (ebantwini) ababenza izenzo ezingcolile, ngempela bona babengabantu abangalungile abaphula umthetho"
  21,75,"Futhi samngenisa emseni wethu, ngempela yena ungowabalungileyo"
  21,76,Kanye noNowa khumbula ngenkathi ememeza ngaphambilini ngakho-ke samphendula sabe sesimsindisa kanye nabantu bakhe ebunzimeni obukhulu
  21,77,Futhi samlekelela ebantwini labo ababephika amavesi ethu ngempela bona babengabantu abangalungile ngakho-ke sabaminzisa bonke
  21,78,Kanye noDavide noSolomoni ngenkathi bobabili bephika isehlulelo mayelana nensimu ngenkathi kwakudle kuyona izimvu zabantu futhi thina sasingofakazi esinqumweni sabo bobabili
  21,79,"Ngakho-ke samenza uSolomoni khumbula ukuthi asiqonde (lesisimo), futhi ngamunye wabo samnikeza ukwahlulela nolwazi, futhi sazenza izintaba, uDavide kanye nezinyoni ukuthi zidumise (uMvelinqangi) futhi thina sasingabenzi (balokho)"
  21,80,Futhi samfundisa ukwenziwa kwezembatho zensimbi zenu ukunivikela ezimpini zenu ngakho-ke ngakube nina ningababongayo yini na
  21,81,Futhi uSolomoni samnika umoya onamandla ohelezayo ngempoqo yakhe ubheke ezweni okuyilona esalibusisa futhi siyizazi zazo zonke izinto
  21,82,Futhi phakathi kosathane kunalabo ababemtshuzela futhi benza nomunye umsebenzi ngaphandle kwalowo futhi sasibaqaphele